{"tid":1817272,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"政府堅持就《禁蒙面法》上訴 一旦成功 預防肺炎不成戴口罩藉口","createTime":"2020-01-09T03:04:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-10T09:27:46.000Z","uid":19552,"like":64,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"cfb101950b117a29228b63b3be943b8eaac267df","tid":1817272,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T03:04:06.000Z","msg":"政府去年引用《緊急法》推出《禁蒙面法》，24名泛民議員及梁國雄向高院提出司法覆核，高院裁定政府做法違反《基本法》。政府及後就案件上訴，高等法院上訴庭今日（9日）起，一連兩日開庭審理，開庭前泛民議員將會見傳媒。《香港01》將直播現場情況。<br />\n<br />\n公民黨立法會議員郭榮鏗會見傳媒時指，《禁蒙面法》對解決現時社會爭議完全沒有作用，加上武漢爆發肺炎，政府上訴要求重啟《禁蒙面法》對市民健康不利，他指政府應「馬上收手，不要一錯再錯。」"},{"pid":"a636a78c67404930c784c5ddfcbe4229f44fa7ae","tid":1817272,"uid":43178,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T03:06:11.000Z","msg":"正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6d6414376f845a05d5f42c748a21023b4c594ca","tid":1817272,"uid":116289,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T03:07:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />攬炒"},{"pid":"b5858ab92685cf216fdf3dcc9a4305086ce3fd6b","tid":1817272,"uid":19552,"like":26,"dislike":2,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T03:07:12.000Z","msg":"好撚柒仆街既政權 咩都政治行先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84dc6b79a0e5bd69868924ab915f510e2bf1fc0a","tid":1817272,"uid":181747,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T03:07:34.000Z","msg":"《禁蒙面法》+支那肺炎=共產黨種族滅絕香港人計劃"},{"pid":"05029398536134438166f3c5fed1db9dbd8220e6","tid":1817272,"uid":8968,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T03:07:46.000Z","msg":"一齊硬食新SARS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkg